 I ask for protection? Did something stick to me?</em></p><p>It's become so common that many ministry teams now automatically pray lengthy cleansing and protection prayers after every session, almost like spiritual hand sanitizer. But what if we're missing something deeper?</p><p>Good questions deserve thoughtful answers. But here's what I've learned: the answer isn't about mastering formulas. It's about learning to live from Jesus' own…</p>"}